data.description: Charming 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Single Family with a 2 Car detached Garage. This very spacious home has many great features including Hardwood Floors throughout living room and bedrooms, large Eat-In Kitchen lovely for entertaining with Granite Counters, gorgeous Porcelain flooring, cook top range, second level offers 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom, private Master Bedroom on 3rd Level with with walk in closet and huge finished attic previously used for children's toy room, basement Family Room with full Jacuzzi Tub and separate Steam Shower with heated flooring. Nice size mud room that leads to huge backyard. Long driveway to 2 car garage with kitchen amenities stainless refrigerator beautifully high quality cabinets and Quartz countertop great for hosting parties or when you are outside enjoying your beautiful 21ft round above ground pool. Freshly Painted throughout and well maintained. Tankless water heater. New furnace installed February 2023. Walking distance to train and schools. No Flood zone.
